      "updated": 1778867517014,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "THE LOOKUP TOOL\n\nThe only door to the document\nlibrary. The researcher asks it a\nquestion; it passes the question to\na separate AI that has read all the\nofficial documents, gets a safe,\nsource-backed answer, and returns\nit - so facts are real, not guessed.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "3238f76btf4boh55",
      "originalText": "THE LOOKUP TOOL\n\nThe only door to the document\nlibrary. The researcher asks it a\nquestion; it passes the question to\na separate AI that has read all the\nofficial documents, gets a safe,\nsource-backed answer, and returns\nit - so facts are real, not guessed.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 12,
      "version": 58,
      "index": "aH",
      "autoResize": true
    },
